snippet.title: [TheFFTVChannel]  Final Fantasy XII International Zodiac Job System, PS2, (1/3)
snippet.description:
Started a Twitch Channel and could use everyone's support! https://www.twitch.tv/thefftvchannel

A tribute and dedication to all of us Final Fantasy fans from around the world. Cheers!
Disclaimer: TheFFTVChannel is unofficial and not sponsored by Square-Enix.  

Get notified by subscribing when more playthough videos are submitted!  Certain Final Fantasy games have different versions, so feel free to look at each of them to see the differences!

None of these videos are intended to be speedruns, and certainly not expertly played.  Also, none of the runs are intended to be 100% completion to encourage viewers that may be interested in the game to pick it up themselves to see the unseen content.
